OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fat first then rain pushes north across
OL,7,Fall parts through the evening.
OL,8,FBecoming dry for a time overnight
OL,9,Fbefore more cloud and patchy light
OL,10,Frain spread into the west through the
OL,11,Fearly hours.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA cloudy morning in the west
OL,14,Fwith some light rain, dry and brighter
OL,15,Fin the east. Bright spells and a few
OL,16,Fshowers through the afternoon. Rain in
OL,17,Fthe evening. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
