OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry, warm and bright in the east over
OL,7,Fthe weekend and on Monday. Cooler and
OL,8,Fcloudier with rain at times in the
OL,9,Fwest.
